Rex In Rome S13 Ep166 - A Voice in the Crowd

A Voice in the Crowd - The illegitimate daughter of a wealthy man becomes the target of her half-sister's plot to kill her to avoid sharing her father's inheritance. Not knowing why she has been targeted, the girl goes into hiding. Meanwhile, Inspector Rivera and Rex set out to find the missing girl. Stars Ettore Bassi.

From Italy, in Italian
